No, no.

04:03.777 --> 04:05.345
All right, let's get off
the bus real quick.

04:05.346 --> 04:06.446
I'm not even surprised.

04:06.447 --> 04:08.315
What the hell?

04:08.316 --> 04:10.450
So, guys, we're gonna
get onto that bus
that is over there,

04:10.451 --> 04:12.752
the white one, and
we're in a bit of
a hurry, okay?

04:12.753 --> 04:15.488
So none of your usual,
you know, thingies,

04:15.489 --> 04:17.123
ten-minute break
